Package mas.customerproxy.plan

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CancelOrderPlan
    Plan to cancel a previously accepted order It updates zone-data of customer with the order to be cancelled.
    ChangeDueDate
    Plan to change due date of the batch.
    CustomerSendNegotiationJobPlan
    Plan to send batch under negotitation This plan updates the negotiation zonedata of customer with batch under negotiation (after making changes from the customer side).
    DispatchJobPlan
    Plan to dispatch generated batch by customer to GSA.
    HandleRejectedOrder
    Plan to handle rejected order from GSA.
    NegotiationGuiPlan
    This plan accepts the batch under negotitation coming from GSA and shows the batch in a GUI where customer can make modifications to this batch
    ReceiveCompletedBatchPlan
    This plan receives the completed batch from GSA.
    RegisterCustomerAgentToBlackboardPlan
    Plan to register customer agent on blackboard.
    SendConfirmedOrderPlan
    Once the batch under negotiation is confirmed by customer, this plan is triggered and it updates the confirmed batch into its zone-data from where other agents are notified
